WEBVTT

00:01.029 --> 00:03.561
Can an established bank move like a start-up?

00:03.977 --> 00:06.700
It's a question we get from some of our largest banking clients.

00:07.351 --> 00:11.248
The face of their business was tellers, then ATMs.

00:11.707 --> 00:13.987
Today it's their mobile app running on the IBM Cloud.

00:15.148 --> 00:16.659
Across every transaction,...

00:16.798 --> 00:20.251
...the hybrid cloud helps their data move quickly and securely.

00:20.943 --> 00:25.669
Our clients are building up features and pushing updates faster on five continents.

00:26.183 --> 00:29.214
With the IBM Cloud, they can move at the speed of any start-up.

